portal.testapp.io)
, including our  Services, hereafter will be collectively referred to as “TestApp.io” and/or “We” and/or “Us”.In this Privacy Policy, everytime we mention "You" and/or “Member” and/or “Developer Member” and/or “Invited Member”, we will be referring to any individual who may access and/or create a Member Account and/or use our Platform and/or App and/or Services.
